<u>As the PCs explore the Glenebon Uplands, you can liven things up with wandering monsters generated from the tables below.</u><br> <br /> 

<i>Take care not to overwhelm the PCs with random encounters, though; it’s usually good to limit wandering monster encounters to only <b>once per day</b>.</i><br> <br />

<br> <br />

There’s a 5% chance of an encounter occurring each time the PCs enter an <b>unclaimed hex</b>, and a 15% chance per day or night spent exploring or camping in an <b>unclaimed hex</b>.<br> <br />
 
As the PCs enter an <b>unclaimed hex</b>, hit the button to see if there is an encounter (5% chance)

<form>
<input type="button" name="Button1" value="Unclaimed Hex Encounter" onClick="this.form.textField1.value = 

tableResults('Hex')" size="" />
<textarea name="textField1" cols="40" rows="1" wrap="soft"></textarea>
</form>

For each day or night cycle spent exploring and <b>unclaimed hex</b>, hit the button to see if there is an encounter (15% chance)

<form>
<input type="button" name="Button2" value="Unclaimed Hex - Day or Night encounter" onClick="this.form.textField1.value = 

tableResults('DayNight')" size="" />
<textarea name="textField1" cols="40" rows="1" wrap="soft"></textarea>
</form>

<br> <br />

These chances decrease to 1% per hex or 5% per day spent exploring or camping in a <b>claimed hex</b>.<br> <br />

As the PCs enter an <b>claimed hex</b>, hit the button to see if there is an encounter (1% chance)

<form>
<input type="button" name="Button3" value="Claimed Hex Encounter" onClick="this.form.textField1.value = 

tableResults('cHex')" size="" />
<textarea name="textField1" cols="40" rows="1" wrap="soft"></textarea>
</form>

For each day or night cycle spent exploring and <b>claimed hex</b>, hit the button to see if there is an encounter (5% chance)

<form>
<input type="button" name="Button4" value="Claimed Hex - Day or Night encounter" onClick="this.form.textField1.value = 

tableResults('cDayNight')" size="" />
<textarea name="textField1" cols="40" rows="1" wrap="soft"></textarea>
</form>

<br> <br />

If there is a random encounter, hit the button of the corresponding terrain to generate an encounter.

